 I have extensively coded the finite element and Isogeometric programs in
 MATLAB for all these works and compared them with Navier, 3D Elasticity,
 and ANSYS solutions to validate the approach.
 I am skilled in Mathematica, C, C++, and Python, with data structure and
 algorithms knowledge.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
I have gained a considerable amount of experience in structural analysis
 and still learning new techniques.
 
